<title>USA: IXC completes $100 mln stock offering.</title>
<headline>IXC completes $100 mln stock offering.</headline>
<dateline>AUSTIN, Texas 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>IXC Communications Inc said Tuesdsay it completed the sale of $100 million of its 7-1/4 percent junior convertible preferred stock due 2007.</p>
<p>The stock was sold to qualified institutional buyers and accredited investors, including the trustees of the General Electric Pension Trust, IXC's largest stockholder, it said.</p>
<p>IXC said net proceeds from the offering will be used to fund capital expenditures and for general corporate purposes.</p>
